like-cat-game-stray-is-finally-coming-to-xbox">有传言称</a>精彩的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/stray-review-ps5-cyberpunk-adventure-cute-cat-173018571.html"><em>《Stray》</em></a>也将登陆 Xbox。 </p><div id="dada01242fe54668ae6c26af4f49bbfc"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/26SMPk8ZyJo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/watch-annapurna-interactives-showcase-here-at-3pm-et-180020145.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/watch-annapurna-interactives-showcase-here-at-3pm-et-180020145.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a446cf8e-fb76-4864-8b7e-3bad587bd6e8</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 18:00:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688065199</ingested><modified> 2023-06-29T19:00:01+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-07/4f7be290-0e8d-11ed-9ef3-77465d13b1ef" width="1527"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-imag